%jdbc(hive)
CREATE TABLE derived_ev_sales AS
SELECT
  e.region AS country,
  e.parameter,
  e.powertrain,
  e.year,
  e.value
FROM
  ev_sales e
WHERE
  e.year >= 2010 AND e.year <= 2018
  AND e.parameter = 'EV sales'
  AND e.region IN ('United Kingdom', 'USA', 'Poland', 'Switzerland', 'Sweden', 'Spain');

    year,
    value

CREATE TABLE sustainability AS
SELECT 
    g.entity, 
    g.electricity_from_hydro, 
    g.electricity_from_solar,
    g.electricity_from_other_renewables,
    e.parameter, 
    e.powertrain,
    e.year,
    e.value

    derived_electricity_prod_by_source_sustainability g
JOIN 
    derived_ev_sales e ON g.entity = e.country;

%jdbc(hive)
CREATE TABLE climate_change AS
SELECT 
    e.country, 
    e.electricity_from_wild_fire,
    e.year,
    g.electricity_from_coal,
    g.electricity_from_gas,
    g.electricity_from_oil,
    g.electricity_from_nuclear
FROM 
    derived_electricity_prod_by_source g
JOIN 
    derived_co2_from_wild_fire e ON g.country = e.country;

%jdbc(hive)
CREATE TABLE climate_change_sustainable_living AS
SELECT
    e.country,
    e.electricity_from_wild_fire,
    e.electricity_from_coal,
    e.electricity_from_gas,
    e.electricity_from_oil,
    e.electricity_from_nuclear,
    g.electricity_from_hydro,
    g.electricity_from_solar,
    g.electricity_from_other_renewables,
    g.parameter,
    g.powertrain,
    g.year,
    g.value
FROM
    sustainability g
JOIN 
    climate_change e ON g.entity = e.country;
